{"tid":1336182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你以為就算我地輸左都會名留青史","createTime":"2019-07-20T21:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T01:01:50.000Z","uid":118312,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2fcbf5112644c4c7dac657acd447bf14a2296f","tid":1336182,"uid":118312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T21:48:33.000Z","msg":"錯喇屌你老母<br />\n支那最撚鐘意刪改歷史<br />\n<br />\n永遠都只會講自己點被迫害<br />\n永遠自己都係受害者<br />\n所以班支那人咁撚愛國就係咁解<br />\n<br />\n聽親嘅歷史都係講自己點俾人打<br />\n八國聯軍，俾日本仔打好慘好慘<br />\n但點解俾人打就隻字不提<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地呢次輸左<br />\n唔單止我地嘅文化同自由都冇左<br />\n我地會係歷史上消失埋<br />\n<br />\n香港人呢次唔撚輸得<br />\n一定要出來屌佢地老母</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac2ff219b51af0f5b1348b05b69af315efa3edc","tid":1336182,"uid":118312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T21:52:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同我出來屌佢老母呀</span>"},{"pid":"331bfc40bdc072c756c2799093b0816ed8eb5b34","tid":1336182,"uid":118312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:01:13.000Z","msg":"唔輸得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e797c01afc5b11f13ea0aee41596c21600296d","tid":1336182,"uid":215876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T22:38:19.000Z","msg":"歷史係由贏家寫出嚟"},{"pid":"1d032ec72e480dc7eba43bf69c6c6c9a73394ce1","tid":1336182,"uid":277155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T23:02:06.000Z","msg":"獨立思考 切勿跟風"},{"pid":"9d579c9d0c5197658c6342cf76e52599d9af74a0","tid":1336182,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T23:04:00.000Z","msg":"真係唔輸得"},{"pid":"b23e27e750ca020ea5f59d6e345fb68d62de8739","tid":1336182,"uid":11447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T23:06:04.000Z","msg":"如果輸左就會變成中共口中嘅 2019年初夏嘅政治風波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h